import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; interface Etablissement { nom: string; nbClasses: string; progression: number; pourcentage: number; } interface Region { nom: string; total: string; pourcentage: number; etablissements: Etablissement[]; } @Component({ selector: 'app-dashboard', templateUrl: './dashboard.component.html', styleUrls: ['./dashboard.component.scss'] }) export class DashboardComponent implements OnInit { selectedEtablissement: string = ''; selectedCommune: string = ''; regions: Region[] = [ { nom: 'COMÈ', total: '45/45', pourcentage: 100, etablissements: [ { nom: 'CEG 2 COMÈ', nbClasses: '12/12', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 }, { nom: 'CEG 4 COMÈ', nbClasses: '11/11', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 }, { nom: 'CEG AKODEHA', nbClasses: '22/22', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 } ] }, { nom: 'BANTÈ', total: '10/16', pourcentage: 60, etablissements: [ { nom: 'CEG 1 BANTÈ', nbClasses: '2/6', progression: 20, pourcentage: 20 }, { nom: 'CEG AKPASSI', nbClasses: '2/4', progression: 50, pourcentage: 50 }, { nom: 'CEG ANOUDE', nbClasses: '6/6', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 } ] }, { nom: 'HOUÉYOGBÉ', total: '20/51', pourcentage: 10, etablissements: [ { nom: 'CEG HOUÉYOGBÉ', nbClasses: '20/24', progression: 45, pourcentage: 45 }, { nom: 'CEG 1 DOUTOU', nbClasses: '4/19', progression: 21, pourcentage: 21 }, { nom: 'CEG AHOULOUMÈ', nbClasses: '3/8', progression: 35, pourcentage: 35 } ] }, { nom: 'SAVALOU', total: '44/44', pourcentage: 100, etablissements: [ { nom: 'CEG 1 SAVALOU', nbClasses: '24/24', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 }, { nom: 'CEG 2 SAVALOU', nbClasses: '11/11', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 }, { nom: 'CEG TCHOGODO', nbClasses: '9/9', progression: 100, pourcentage: 100 } ] } ]; constructor() { } ngOnInit(): void { } getProgressBarColor(pourcentage: number): string { if (pourcentage >= 100) return 'bg-green-500'; if (pourcentage >= 50) return 'bg-yellow-500'; return 'bg-red-500'; } }
